MutationTesting

Class Program

  • java.lang.Object
    • MutationTesting.Program

  • public class Program
extends Object
    Program model object. We use this to store the gold version of our program.

    A program consists primarily of source files and various supporting documents, such as build configuration and comparison files.

    Each mutant version is created by duplicating and modifying the gold version Program instance.

    Author:
    jbreeden
